    {
        "url": "/quotes/charles_c_mann_877988",
        "quote": "Americans are willing to cheer on politicians who denounce bureaucratic overreach and job-killing red tape in abstract terms. But they turn out to like specific regulations against toxic chemicals in their drinking water.",
